org.netbeans.modules.classfile

Class StackMapFrame.SameLocals1StackItemFrame

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.netbeans.modules.classfile.StackMapFrame
      • org.netbeans.modules.classfile.StackMapFrame.SameLocals1StackItemFrame
  • Enclosing class:
    StackMapFrame

    public static final class StackMapFrame.SameLocals1StackItemFrame
extends StackMapFrame
    A frame type of same_locals_1_stack_item_frame, which means that the frame has exactly the same locals as the previous stack map frame and that the number of stack items is 1.
